# 🚌 Intelligent Bus Ticket Booking System

## 📌 Project Overview

The Intelligent Bus Ticket Booking System is a smart web-based application that helps users search, book, and manage bus tickets efficiently. The system uses intelligent features such as route recommendations, seat availability tracking, fare estimation, and automated booking management to provide a seamless travel experience.

## 🎯 Objectives

* Simplify bus ticket booking.
* Provide real-time seat availability.
* Recommend suitable buses based on user preferences.
* Reduce manual booking efforts.
* Improve user experience through automation.

## ✨ Features

* User Registration and Login
* Search Buses by Source and Destination
* Real-Time Seat Availability
* Online Ticket Booking
* Fare Calculation
* Booking History
* Ticket Cancellation
* Smart Bus Recommendations
* Admin Dashboard for Bus Management

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

### Frontend

* HTML5
* CSS3
* JavaScript
* Bootstrap

### Backend

* Python
* Flask

### Database

* MySQL / SQLite

### Version Control

* Git & GitHub

## 🏗️ System Architecture

User → Web Interface → Flask Backend → Database

The user interacts with the web interface, which communicates with the Flask backend. The backend processes requests, retrieves data from the database, and returns booking information to the user.

